list

  1/4 red onion, diced
  1 jalapeno, diced
  1 lime's juice
  2 cloves garlic
  1/2 tsp kosher salt
  1 tomato, diced
  4 avocados
  1/4 cup cilantro, minced

directions

  add onion, jalapeno, lime juice, garlic, salt to molcajete
    grind to paste
  add tomatoes, avocados, cilantro to molcajete
    grind roughly
